CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 10, 1945, pg. 22, reads: "Birthday Dinner - Mrs. Dorie Andrews celebrated her birthday with a dinner party, at Parker's, last Friday. Those attending were Mrs. M. Thornton, R. Blockwell, Mrs. M. West, Mrs. M. Hudson, Miss Dorie Andrews, William Hardy, Mrs. L. Moore, E. Alexander, Mrs. M. Turner and Mrs. O. McGlory. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group at Parker's restaurant celebrating birthday of Dorie Andrews, including M. Thornton, R. Blockwell, M. West, M. Hudson, Dorie Andrews, William Hardy, L. Moore, E. Alexander, M. Turner and O. McGlory gathered around table
